<th rowspan="2"><a href="/wiki/Pixel_aspect_ratio" title="Pixel aspect ratio">Pixel aspect ratio</a></th>
<th rowspan="2">Form of scanning</th>
<th rowspan="2">Framerate (<a href="/wiki/Hertz" title="Hertz">Hz</a>)</th>
</tr>
<tr style="background:#eee;">
<th>Vertical</th>
<th>Horizontal</th>
