<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Chile.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Chile.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Flag_of_Chile.svg/22px-Flag_of_Chile.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Chile" title="Chile">Chile</a> (experimental)</li>
