<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Mexico.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Mexico.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Flag_of_Mexico.svg/22px-Flag_of_Mexico.svg.png" width="22" height="13" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Mexico" title="Mexico">Mexico</a> (To be completely transformed by January 1, 2016)</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Peru.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Peru.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Flag_of_Peru.svg/22px-Flag_of_Peru.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Peru" title="Peru">Peru</a> (experimental only in <a href="/wiki/Lima_Metropolitan_Area" title="Lima Metropolitan Area">Lima</a>)</li>
