<ul>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Puerto_Rico.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Puerto Rico.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Flag_of_Puerto_Rico.svg/22px-Flag_of_Puerto_Rico.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Puerto_Rico" title="Puerto Rico">Puerto Rico</a> (To be completely transformed by June 12, 2009, except LPTV)</li>
