0i" title="1080i">1080i</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/1080p" title="1080p">1080p</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Serial_digital_interface" title="Serial digital interface">Serial digital interface</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Smart_antenna" title="Smart antenna">Smart antennas</a> (<a href="/wiki/CEA-909" title="CEA-909">CEA-909</a>)</span></div>
